images.name: La Salle Explorers vs. Richmond Spiders: Game Highlights
images.caption: La Salle Explorers vs. Richmond Spiders: Game Highlights

article.linkText: Bailey's 22 help Richmond defeat La Salle 82-65
article.story: RICHMOND, Va. -- — Dji Bailey's 22 points helped Richmond defeat La Salle 82-65 on Saturday. Bailey also contributed seven rebounds for the Spiders (17-6, 9-1 Atlantic 10 Conference). Isaiah Bigelow scored 17 points and added six rebounds. Jordan King shot 5 for 10, including 3 for 5 from beyond the arc to finish with 13 points. Khalil Brantley led the way for the Explorers (11-13, 2-9) with 22 points and two steals. Daeshon Shepherd added 12 points for La Salle. In addition, Jhamir Brickus finished with 12 points and four assists. Led by eight first-half points from Neal Quinn, Richmond carried a 36-27 lead into the break. Richmond took the lead for what would be the final time on Bigelow's 3-pointer with 9:39 remaining in the second half. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
